<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-6"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">
  
  <!-- Header -->
  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>
  <div class="mb-8 p-4 p-6">     
    <p class="mb-4">Le frazioni con <strong>denominatore 10, 100, 1000</strong>... si chiamano <strong>frazioni decimali</strong>, ma anche le frazioni che hanno denominatori diversi possono essere trasformate in <strong>frazioni decimali equivalenti</strong>.</p>
    <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p065/p065_01.jpg", alt: "Trasformazione frazioni" %>
    <p class="mb-4">Dunque, puoi scrivere 3/5 anche in altri modi:</p>
    <p class="mb-4">con una frazione decimale equivalente, a parole e con un numero decimale.</p>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-8  mb-4">  
      <div class="text-center">  
        <div class="font-bold  mb-2">6</div>
  
        <div class="mb-2"></div>
  
        <div class="font-bold ">10</div>
       </div>
      <div>sei decimi</div>
  
      <div class="font-bold ">0,6</div>
     </div>
    <p class="text-gray-600">I numeri "con la virgola", come sai, si chiamano <strong>numeri decimali</strong>.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-8 p-4 p-6">     
    <h3 class="font-bold  mb-4">â€¢ Prova tu.</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">Trasforma la frazione 4/25 in una frazione decimale equivalente.</p>
    <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p065/p065_02.jpg", alt: "Esercizio trasformazione" %>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4 p-6">     
    <h2 class=" font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">ESERCIZI</h2>
    <div class="p-4 mb-4" data-controller="fill-blanks">       
      <h3 class=" font-bold mb-3">
        <span class="bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full   inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
        Trasforma le frazioni date in frazioni decimali equivalenti.
      </h3>
      <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p065/p065_03.jpg", alt: "Esercizio 1" %>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4">       
      <h3 class=" font-bold mb-3">
        <span class="bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full   inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
        Trasforma le frazioni date in frazioni decimali equivalenti, poi esprimile a parole e con un numero decimale. Esegui sul quaderno.
      </h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center ">         <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>3</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 full my-0.5"></span><span>4</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>3</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 full my-0.5"></span><span>5</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>2</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 full my-0.5"></span><span>4</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>14</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 full my-0.5"></span><span>25</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>13</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 full my-0.5"></span><span>50</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>45</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 full my-0.5"></span><span>300</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center"><span>1</span><span class="border-t border-gray-600 full my-0.5"></span><span>25</span></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <p class="text-red-600 font-bold ">Quaderno esercizi pp. 209, 213</p>
  </div>
   <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'purple' %>
</div>
